name: Llostal
description:
Third stop of my Interstellar Journey; I had a hard time landing here, the terrain is very irregular, and it has bright and colorful lines all over the floor that make it disorienting to see. Even with this obstacle, the view is worth the effort, the lines feel like they are leading me somewhere, but I don't know where yet, and there is a crystal calling out to me, but I'm not sure if I want to get any closer than this.
